","label":"mentions"},{"source":"receDR6PLl8FxyIRO","target":"rec1RMZhQrrzq5oHJ","label":"mentions"},{"source":"receDR6PLl8FxyIRO","target":"recjkmUO88wihv8Ci","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recdnX3XcmeYbsr0M","ref":"Exod.7.1","text":"And the LORD said unto Moses, See, I have made thee a god to Pharaoh: and Aaron thy brother shall be thy prophet.","year":-1491},{"id":"rechjKTHqlRNRePT9","ref":"Exod.7.2","text":"Thou shalt speak all that I command thee: and Aaron thy brother shall speak unto Pharaoh, that he send the children of Israel out of his land.","year":-1491},{"id":"rec5D4U4VisM9WHA7","ref":"Exod.7.3","text":"And I will harden Pharaoh’s heart, and multiply my signs and my wonders in the land of Egypt.","year":-1491},{"id":"recXluxfNcBruHQtN","ref":"Exod.7.4","text":"But Pharaoh shall not hearken unto you, that I may lay my hand upon Egypt, and bring forth mine armies, and my people the children of Israel, out of the land of Egypt by great judgments.","year":-1491},{"id":"rec28g0dPVLGJeARX","ref":"Exod.7.5","text":"And the Egyptians shall know that I am the LORD, when I stretch forth mine hand upon Egypt, and bring out the children of Israel from among them.","year":-1491},{"id":"recOQ1tEfeehpEDE3","ref":"Exod.7.6","text":"And Moses and Aaron did as the LORD commanded them, so did they.","year":-1491},{"id":"recmDRsM2utlLwRem","ref":"Exod.7.7","text":"And Moses was fourscore years old, and Aaron fourscore and three years old, when they spake unto Pharaoh.","year":-1491},{"id":"rec97rPoJWIikLbM2","ref":"Exod.7.8","text":"And the LORD spake unto Moses and unto Aaron, saying,","year":-1491}]}
